CLOSURE_REASON: Case Closed. Closed date : 2015-11-12 15:34:50.297 Case Referred to External Agency Thank you for contacting DCR. The agency does regularly empty that barrel. We are finding that it gets filled more frequently  due to its proximity to both the Garden (There was a game there last night) and the active construction site of the Converse World Headquarters (the construction workers tend to eat their lunch at that park) so the level of trash that accumulates is larger and more frequent than a barrel that is in a park during the late fall season.      That being said  DCR Community Relations and field staff are working to get the barrel emptied on a more frequent basis. Please contact the agency with any further questions or concerns.       Have a good day        Bill Hickey DCR Community Relations
